# Gitleaks ignore patterns
# Patterns to exclude from secrets scanning

# Test files with mock secrets
**/test/**/*.json
**/tests/**/*.json
**/*_test.go
**/*_test.py
**/*.test.js
**/__tests__/**/*

# Documentation examples
**/docs/**/*.md
**/examples/**/*
**/samples/**/*

# Configuration templates
**/*.template
**/*.example
**/*.sample
**/.env.example
**/.env.template

# Lock files
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/poetry.lock
**/Pipfile.lock
**/go.sum

# Build artifacts
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/target/**
**/.next/**
**/node_modules/**

# IDE and editor files
**/.idea/**
**/.vscode/**
**/.vs/**

# OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Specific known false positives
**/vendor/**
**/third_party/**

# CI/CD configuration (may contain masked secrets)
**/.github/workflows/*.yml
**/.gitlab-ci.yml
**/.circleci/config.yml

# Kubernetes secrets (already encrypted/managed)
**/k8s/**/secret.yaml
**/k8s/**/sealed-secret.yaml

# Terraform state files
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*

# Log files
**/*.log
